name: spring-mvc-angular-js-hibernate-bootstrap-java-single-page-jwt-auth-rest-api-webapp-framework
description: This project provides sample hibernate entities, spring data entities, angularjs mvc code, models, exception handling interceptors, repositories, services and controllers classes. The UI for the default simple web project bundled in this framework is built using Twiiter Bootstrap and AngularJS Single Page App. The projects brings together Java, Spring 4, Spring MVC 4, Spring JPA, Hibernate, Angular JS, Twitter Bootstrap, JWT Token Authentication technology in a clean easy to use fashion.
